snippet.title: Heavy Metal Machines
snippet.description:
Play for free now on Steam: https://goo.gl/FR9R8c

Enter the post-apocalyptic world of Heavy Metal Machines, an ONLINE and FREE MULTIPLAYER game that unites action, car-chases, and battles in an extremely competitive setting. Meet the Metal City and all our characters in this game that is much more than a MOBA.

***Follow us***
instagram.com/officialhmm
facebook.com/heavymetalmachines

***Blog***
http://heavymetalmachines.com/blog

----------------

Jogue agora de graça no Steam: https://goo.gl/FR9R8c
